gcf - Git Changed Files

USAGE:
    gcf [-ref=reference] [-since=commit] [-before=commit]

DESCRIPTION:
    Show changed files with optional filtering by git reference and date range.

OPTIONS:
    -ref=reference
        Git reference to compare against

    -since=commit
        Show commits after this reference

    -before=commit
        Show commits before this reference

EXAMPLES:
    gcf
    gcf -ref=main
    gcf -since=v1.0.0 -before=v2.0.0
